@dumbolts -- you don't want to set uploads to unlimited or it will slow downloads down due to the overhead involved with high speed downloads -- you need to leave about 10% of your upload capacity for the connections to send communication to each other for the send\receive signals - but you also do not want to set it too low or you are not sharing a good % and it's not right to hit and run -- so best to set the max upload to about 10% under your available upload bandwidth to keep your downloads fast but still share at good speed also !
